amuels wife marjorie margie samuels gave the whiskey its name drew its label and thought up the wax dipping that gives the bottle its distinctive look it was introduced to the market in  three varieties are marketed the original a mint julep flavor with green wax on the neck released seasonally in limited amounts and  a variety flavored by introducing seared french oak staves into the traditional charred white oak barrel toward the end of its aging the original has been bottled at  us proof  alcohol by volume makers mark is along with george dickel and old forester one of a handful of americanmade whiskies that uses the scottish spelling whisky rather than the predominant american whiskey bourbon house  loungeedit makers mark bourbon house and lounge in fourth street live louisville makers mark has began creating branded restaurants with the october  opening of makers mark bourbon house  lounge in the fourth street live entertainment complex in downtown louisville kentucky in addition to serving makers mark it features bourbons from each of kentuckys distilleries the menu was designed by chef al paris of the famous zanzibar blue restaurant in philadelphia a second such establishment opened in kansas city missouris downtown power  light district in  and a third at the indiana live casino in shelbyville indiana just outside indianapolis in march  reviewsedit the production line at the makers mark distillery in loretto kentucky makers mark bourbon has earned solid marks at international spirit ratings competitions its primary bourbon earned a gold medal at the  san francisco world spirit ratings competition and a score of – from wine enthusiast in  the makers mark —which benefits from longer aging and exposure to toasted french oak staves—has earned similar ratings jane macquitty spirits writer for the london times said of makers mark that what separates this bourbon from the rest is the softness and smoothness of its rich oak vanilla and raisinylike flavours food critic morgan murphy said dark as its red wax seal this beautiful whiskey packs apple spice vanilla and a frontofthemouth crispness that is admired the world over limited edition collectors setsedit keenelandedit makers mark began special edition bottles featuring keeneland bottles for horses in  the label was white with a dark green horse and green wax other keeneland bottles include famous derby winners such as secretariat  seattle slew  affirmed  and american pharoah  university of louisvilleedit on july   makers mark started selling a limited edition bottle featuring university of louisvilles head football coach charlie strong the bottles were created to raise money for a new academic center of excellence on uofls campus makers mark also has marketed special label bottles with the images of hall of fame basketball coach rick pitino and dynamic athletic tom jurich for the same purpose university of kentuckyedit makers mark has featured several university of kentucky sports personalities on its university of kentucky uk line of limited release bottles a limited quantity of bottles can be signed for free by the personality that was selected for the bottle and by a member of the samuels family the signing party is held at keeneland horse track in the universitys home city of lexington the first uk special edition bottle was produced in  in celebration of the  ncaa mens basketball champions makers mark printed a bottle that had a denim background with white type the teams coach at the time rick pitino signed the bottle other bottles include wildcat bottle  bill keightley  rupps runts  the unforgettables  joe b hall first in  and again in  rich brooks  john calipari  tim couch  dan issel  mark stoops  and adolph rupp  the  bottle was the first in a series honoring the five basketball coaches who won ncaa titles at uk future entries in the series will feature pitino in  tubby smith in  and calipari for a second time in  see alsoedit jack daniels jim beam evan williams early times referencesedit  makers mark wax makers mark retrieved    a b c d samuels to step down as makers mark president archived july   at the wayback machine bruce schreiner associated press  january   a b riddle becky old grist mill and distillery kentucky historical society retrieved    it tastes expensive  and is tradeark description page trademarkia accessed   makers mark review page at bourbon central bourboncentralcom retrieved    httpwwwwfplorgpostmarkersmarkcoorobsamuelsextremelyshortsupplyledreductionalcoholvolumepermanent dead link  wilson jason february   makers mark debacle the proof is in the overreaction washington post retrieved april     makers mark waters down bourbon to meet demand cbs moneywatch associated press february   retrieved april     otts chris february   makers mark defends watering down its bourbon usa today retrieved april     irwin neil february   bourbonomics  what the makers mark dilution debacle says about corporate strategy washington post retrieved april     cooper rachel  february  makers mark reverses move to water down whisky the daily telegraph retrieved  march    makers mark to restore alcohol content of whiskey archived december   at the wayback machine  no change to makers mark abv in australia beam  the shout hotel news liquor news bar  club news   schreiner bruce  january  maker of jim beam makers mark bought by japanese company knox news retrieved  march    chumley cheryl k  january  jim beam makers mark to be sold to japanese company consumers told nothing has changed the washington times retrieved  february    hahn fritz october   this thing you should try makers mark cask strength bourbon the washington post retrieved august     hayes annie  july  beam suntory gtr unveils makers mark cask strength the spirits business retrieved august     schreiner bruce november   crank up the flow of red wax makers mark is boosting its bourbon output us news  world report louisville kentucky associated press retrieved november     